nelId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"#support","cachedResultName":"#support"},"text":"=🚨 {{ $json.workflow }} failed at {{ $json.failedNode }}: {{ $json.errorMessage }}","otherOptions":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.slack","typeVersion":2.3,"position":[3334,1420],"id":"46e3c41b-a467-4c60-a0f9-28969440963c","name":"Escalate Failure to Slack","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"content":"### Receive Inbound Webhook\n\nEntry point: listens for POST calls on `/wf07585-conversation`. Use the TEST url while building, switch callers to the PRODUCTION url after publishing.\n\nNext: Stamp & Shape Conversation","width":280,"height":232,"color":5},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-330,520],"id":"841a86de-1164-7989-bb35-ebcfd005afb5","name":"Note: Receive Inbound Webhook"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Stamp & Shape Conversation\n\nShapes the item: writes `sessionId`, `receivedAt`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Payload Valid?","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,520],"id":"bb38d958-67d7-74bf-1b49-1b1ab93c4f04","name":"Note: Stamp & Shape Conversation"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Payload Valid?\n\nTwo-way gate on `={{ $json.sessionId }}`. TRUE continues the happy path, FALSE takes the alternate branch.\n\nPorts: ①→ Frame the Assignment · ②→ Record Rejected Input","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,520],"id":"55683121-66d2-6952-0e4e-a61443c99bc2","name":"Note: Payload Valid?"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Record Rejected Input\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,1030],"id":"895e26f6-cf82-de8b-e90d-4da3657c6ad6","name":"Note: Record Rejected Input"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Frame the Assignment\n\nShapes the item: writes `assignment`, `deadline`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Coordinator Agent","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[642,520],"id":"93e77a2f-3a1c-fbd8-31a1-a1204e0306a6","name":"Note: Frame the Assignment"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Coordinator Agent\n\nThe AI brain: reads the input, decides which attached tools to call (and in what order), then composes the answer.\n\nPorts: ①→ Unpack Sections · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n⚠ failures exit via the error rail","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[966,520],"id":"e478b761-48fc-8507-c7ac-767f5db20fa2","name":"Note: Coordinator Agent"},{"parameters":{"content":"### OpenAI Chat Model\n\nChat model powering the AI step (model: `gpt-4o-mini`). Swap providers here without rewiring.\n\nFeeds **Coordinator Agent** as `languageModel`\n\n🔑 OpenAI API key","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1209,1090],"id":"caf94a3d-1e3b-a559-cb36-3a5541ff1bd2","name":"Note: OpenAI Chat Model"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Research Specialist (Sub-workflow)\n\nSpecialist sub-workflow exposed as a callable tool — one narrow capability per tool.\n\nFeeds **Coordinator Agent** as `tool`","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1128,1510],"id":"d494e711-e25a-8712-ad4b-1f876ba0dcd8","name":"Note: Research Specialist (Sub-workflow)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Draft Specialist (Sub-workflow)\n\nSpecialist sub-workflow exposed as a callable tool — one narrow capability per tool.\n\nFeeds **Coordinator Agent** as `tool`","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1384,1750],"id":"4079dbeb-e178-cc31-75c7-578fefc1654e","name":"Note: Draft Specialist (Sub-workflow)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Review Specialist (Sub-workflow)\n\nSpecialist sub-workflow exposed as a callable tool — one narrow capability per tool.\n\nFeeds **Coordinator Agent** as `tool`","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1816,1510],"id":"4dc7f8f9-43a9-01da-58ac-7f421da41401","name":"Note: Review Specialist (Sub-workflow)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Enforce Result Schema\n\nForces the agent's answer into the JSON schema below — downstream nodes rely on this exact shape.\n\nFeeds **Coordinator Agent** as `outputParser`","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1978,1090],"id":"5e0f2c37-c025-3d26-a7e2-1b9c105d12e1","name":"Note: Enforce Result Schema"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Unpack Sections\n\nExplodes the `output.sections` array into one item per element.\n\nNext: Persist Deliverable to Google Sheets","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2302,520],"id":"dad3abb8-582a-1e70-e2cf-5f6f6a3ead75","name":"Note: Unpack Sections"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Persist Deliverable to Google Sheets\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Summarize Run Stats · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2626,520],"id":"752feea5-6622-f4f3-a2d0-6787544d73aa","name":"Note: Persist Deliverable to Google Sheets"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Run Stats\n\nShapes the item: writes `runAt`, `itemCount`, `status`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2950,520],"id":"0d967f01-dc20-765e-2a47-fbe11c7df3fa","name":"Note: Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Send Summary to Slack · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3274,520],"id":"8819bada-b100-76fd-1832-69cb25e12093","name":"Note: Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3598,520],"id":"c162b002-4ced-8bd1-f598-89b27fde74ec","name":"Note: Send Summary to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Slack","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2950,1540],"id":"50d4b5bd-dd97-9d22-e174-c4756e85eb8f","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3274,1540],"id":"703d7e4d-71b8-a860-f53c-1844e18966a5","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Automate an assistant workflow with Gmail end to end\n\n**Pattern:** AI Agent · **Level:** Advanced · **Trigger:** Webhook\n\n## What it does\nAutomate an assistant workflow with Gmail end to end. It fires the moment an external system calls its webhook.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual faq bots is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nReceive Inbound Webhook → Stamp & Shape Conversation → Payload Valid? → Frame the Assignment → Coordinator Agent → Unpack Sections → Persist Deliverable to Google Sheets → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to ai agent without manual effort\n- Anyone automating faq bots in customer support\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Runs 24/7 in the background\n- Scales without extra headcount\n- Saves hours of manual work each week\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: Google OAuth2 / service account; OpenAI API key; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"883e1362-9f33-7c14-c4ce-78dc639b47bf","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-20],"id":"ddd16c4e-78fc-9bef-e599-dbe1fe498907","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🔐 Security\n\nNever trust inbound payloads: the webhook path is unguessable. Add header auth or IP allow-listing for defense in depth. Secrets live in n8n credentials — never in node parameters.","width":360,"height":260,"color":1},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-20],"id":"0ca8b073-c56d-446e-401d-b94fbcfc5021","name":"🔐 Security"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🤖 AI cluster\n\nPurple nodes form one AI unit: the root node orchestrates, sub-nodes plug in via typed ports (model / memory / tools / parser). Swap the chat model without rewiring anything else. Costs scale with tokens — keep prompts lean and cap iterations.","width":360,"height":260,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[610,-20],"id":"4ce7941e-d90b-21c3-2ddc-7c5c380e6d82","name":"🤖 AI cluster"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your faq bots process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1030,-20],"id":"0526e367-bbe2-9c2f-acec-6e93f7746e8e","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"Receive Inbound Webhook":{"main":[[{"node":"Stamp & Shape Conversation","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Stamp & Shape Conversation":{"main":[[{"node":"Payload Valid?","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Payload Valid?":{"main":[[{"node":"Frame the Assignment","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Record Rejected Input","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Frame the Assignment":{"main":[[{"node":"Coordinator Agent","type":"main","index":0}]]},"OpenAI Chat Model":{"ai_languageModel":[[{"node":"Coordinator Agent","type":"ai_languageModel","index":0}]]},"Research Specialist (Sub-workflow)":{"ai_tool":[[{"node":"Coordinator Agent","type":"ai_tool","index":0}]]},"Draft Specialist (Sub-workflow)":{"ai_tool":[[{"node":"Coordinator Agent","type":"ai_tool","index":0}]]},"Review Specialist (Sub-workflow)":{"ai_tool":[[{"node":"Coordinator Agent","type":"ai_tool","index":0}]]},"Enforce Result Schema":{"ai_outputParser":[[{"node":"Coordinator Agent","type":"ai_outputParser","index":0}]]},"Coordinator Agent":{"main":[[{"node":"Unpack Sections","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Unpack Sections":{"main":[[{"node":"Persist Deliverable to Google Sheets","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Persist Deliverable to Google Sheets":{"main":[[{"node":"Summarize Run Stats","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Summarize Run Stats":{"main":[[{"node":"Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Append Audit Row (Google Sheets)":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Summary to Slack","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Capture Failure Context":{"main":[[{"node":"Escalate Failure to Slack","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Summary to Slack":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"81526380-6c8d-4f23-8882-4e301d74a71b","id":"FDX07585"}